headline: CPI Aerostructures Announces Dorith Hakim’s Appointment to the Aerospace Industry Association’s Executive Committee
summary: EDGEWOOD, N.Y., Dec. 05, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- CPI Aerostructures, Inc. (“CPI Aero®” or the “Company”) (NYSE American: CVU) announced today that Dorith Hakim has been appointed to the Aerospace Industry Association’s Executive Committee. AIA is the primary trade association and advocacy group for the U.S. aerospace and defense industry, representing a wide range of member companies.
